==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coventry
<hw>Cov"en*try</hw> <pr>(k?v"<it>e</it>n-tr?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
town in the county of Warwick, England.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To send to Coventry</b></col>, <cd>to exclude from
society; to shut out from social intercourse, as for ungentlemanly
conduct.</cd> -- <col><b>Coventry blue</b></col>, <cd>blue thread of a
superior dye, made at Coventry, England, and used for
embroidery.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cover</ent>⟦br⟧
